Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha at last broke through\NNaraku's barrier!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:44.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But before he could render\nthe final blow,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:46.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku, who had been seriously\ninjured, escaped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:54.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was only because Naraku resorted\nto a dastardly trick using Kohaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:59.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But who would have thought that\NSesshomaru would save Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But with Naraku's disappearance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:09.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we were actually grateful\nfor the brief respite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Especially Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our journey's aim is to destroy Naraku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and gather all the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:18.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We continue onward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:25.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd better back down,\nor I'll get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Short-tempered as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:28.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sending your wolves at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have a grudge or something\nagainst me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:57.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that Ayame, the granddaughter\nof the Wolf-Demon Tribe elder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:01.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard she went north with\nthe elder a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ayame?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came to give you\NGramps' message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Message?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're going to take me\nfor your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:14.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have a Sacred Jewel shard\nin your possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:22.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With that, you'll be worthy\nof ruling the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So come with me\nand let's get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Don't joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why should I marry you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:32.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:39.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You promised to marry me when\NI came down from the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, when'd you make\nsuch a promise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gramps told me to bring you back,\nwith force if necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!\NWe're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let go of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I already have a fiancée\nnamed Kagome who's gonna marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:27.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have made any promises\nto marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fiancée?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:38.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey wait, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Has he really forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He {\i1}promised....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On the night of the lunar rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Naraku's whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We checked everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there were no rumors\nabout a demon named Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:22.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems Inuyasha hasn't caught\nany scent of Naraku either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe that a demonic aura\nthat strong could disappear so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't be helped if you\ncan't smell anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:38.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you don't sense\nthe Sacred Jewel shards either?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:44.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No sense getting overly worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we just keep collecting\nthe Sacred Jewel shards as usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:49.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure Naraku will come after\nthem himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't just wait around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I wonder how many\nmore shards there {\i1}are....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:02.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,besides the ones\nthat Naraku has in his possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have three shards here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:12.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then there's the one\nimbedded in Kohaku's back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Koga has a couple, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was quite a long time {\i1}ago....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he DID promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't overdo it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when it gets to\nbe too hard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:56.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make you my wife, Ayame.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was still a {\i1}child....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So if Koga doesn't remember,\NI guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe I should return\nto the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My territory is being overrun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:30.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without the Sacred Jewel,\nwe cannot overcome this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:35.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find Koga and bring him here\nas soon as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:47.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to try one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:02.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This castle reeks with\NNaraku's scent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's no miasma or\nany sign of him at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This mark...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:16.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koga, the castle is\ntotally empty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:18.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find the mutt and\nquestion him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:26.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That mutt's smell also\nlingers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:29.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something happened between\nhim and Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha might know something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't leave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:44.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku isn't here.\NBut if he's nearby...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's sure to come after me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the Sacred Jewel shards\nin my legs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know. Koga was here\nwithout a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this place? It gives\nme the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:55.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was that demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ginta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's Ayame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why's she here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you two! What were you doing\nin that creepy castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:07.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did it appear from\NNaraku's castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's....castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:27.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't know because you've\nbeen in the mountains with the elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just recently, our comrades in\nthe north and east were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:34.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the one behind it is\na demon named Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga has been looking for\NNaraku to get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}didn't....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:48.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That whirlwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:02.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I thought I smelled\nsomething unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's upset already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Koga! Coming here\nto flirt with Kagome again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:10.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Kagome!\NHow've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:25.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey mutt! Where's Naraku?\N'Fess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that your business here, Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then quit flirting around\nwith Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just answer my question, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:38.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're still looking for Naraku, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did Naraku abandon his castle\nand run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna know, Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:50.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's 'cuz I busted through\NNaraku's barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With my Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:57.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Shocked?\NServes you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:14:03.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More than shocked! You got that close,\nand you let Naraku escape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:12.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I had been there,\NI'd have destroyed Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:15.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!\NIf I let you go {\i1}on....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jumping to dumb {\i1}conclusions....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A {\i1}miasma....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Naraku's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's something {\i1}weird....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,coming from Naraku's castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:54.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Another incarnation of\NNaraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a Hair Demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what was in\nthe castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:22.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No mistake about it!\NAyame saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ayame?\NShe was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I dunno!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We got separated when\nwe started running.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:31.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why didn't I sense this\ndemon sooner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred Jewel {\i1}shards....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:49.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This pile of hair is after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:49.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're an ugly {\i1}bastard....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it looks like you can talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:08.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such brute strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer me!\NWhere is Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mutt! You can take care\nof the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take Kagome to\na safe place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:30.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!\NThe nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:44.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:48.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It wasn't too strong for\na demon created by Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:52.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it went over on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Its goal is the Sacred Jewel\nshards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:56.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where're you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:02.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where? Someplace where the\ndemon won't come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:14.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ayame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:15.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ayame?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:18.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a mortal woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have time to\nexplain to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:32.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome....That's the fiancée\nyou mentioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,F-Fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Koga's!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga?!\NWhy'd you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's only natural\nsince I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't just decide things\nlike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:48.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga is my fiancé!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if you can use\nyour tricks on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep it up,\nand I'll get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Falling in love with\na mortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's your Wolf-Demon Tribe pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! I love Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have no right\nto tell me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:16.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ka-go-me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:21.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It sounds like my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only the final syllable "me."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:30.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you want to\nmarry that girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can't go against\nthe tribe's code!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A code made up by\nthe elders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:40.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When did I ever say\NI'd marry you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,promised {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:51.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,on the night of\nthe lunar {\i1}rainbow....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lunar rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the moon appears at night...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:01.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do rainbows come out\nat night?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was when I was\nstill a {\i1}child....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}During the training Gramps\nhad instructed me to do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got lost near the nest of\nthe Birds of Paradise demons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was about to be devoured.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey....{\i0}\NCome with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The elder is worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It must not be easy being\nthe elder's granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he going to\nthe northern mountains, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:36.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0} He said he\nwould train me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:42.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're going to use that\nflower in training?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:44.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It has the same name\nas {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:49.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I'm taking it to\nthe mountains, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Umm...\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:03.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it gets too hard,\NI'll make you my wife, Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:05.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:08.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, when you come down\nfrom the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A lunar rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Is that {\i1}true....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did I really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's such a romantic story!\NAnd you don't remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I kept those words\nin my {\i1}heart....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:57.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and endured all the training with Gramps,\nand lived in the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:58.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:02.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can you forget such words?!\NYou're despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:03.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:50.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:52.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You let Naraku's demon go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:54.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the stupid one, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're Ayame's fiancé!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you flirt\nwith Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:59.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't hide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:04.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whether it's arranged or not,\nshe's gonna be your bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:07.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NI still have things to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:11.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Koga's Bride-To-Be"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.83,0:24:13.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry {\i1}Ayame....{\i0}\NThat's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop the act, stupid wolf!
